{"tid":854543,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［發春］單身咗咁耐 突然間搵到個好中意女仔 點做好？","createTime":"2018-10-09T12:13:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T16:49:45.000Z","uid":89402,"like":7,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"62102d1306edad4bfa97ebf06325658f7aa36a47","tid":854543,"uid":89402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T12:13:57.000Z","msg":"無拍拖咁耐 都已經慣左自已一個<br />\n做咩事都覺得一個人好啲 <br />\n好自由既感覺<br />\n已經寡到昅囡都難得昅既地步<br />\n突然間 遇上了她<br />\n佢做保安既<br />\n所以每朝都會係棟大廈見到佢<br />\n佢一笑笑口講早晨完之後<br />\n人都特別精神<br />\n佢既笑容真係好笑得靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到比佢點燃起心中少少既火花<br />\n每一日一做完嘢<br />\n有空聊既時間就會諗起佢諗起佢個笑容..."},{"pid":"888de12d4eb3faa39532b38d110ad0c82ece6851","tid":854543,"uid":9450,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T12:15:16.000Z","msg":"拎電話 <br />\n完"},{"pid":"d203cfa00e6e6e9b0ec06a7b81e61e2f4a5a4d36","tid":854543,"uid":89402,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T12:16:05.000Z","msg":"但係明知無可能..<br />\n<br />\n我文員仔一個 搵得個咁少人工<br />\n邊搵到大錢養佢啊<br />\n<br />\n唉無架啦 真係唔好發咁多夢"},{"pid":"50183b484224f2c9f9976e783cef6e3c64fe630a","tid":854543,"uid":29070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T12:16:51.000Z","msg":"試下拎contact囉"},{"pid":"01bdfcd4a4099f9ed07fddeca7acce88d7d9713e","tid":854543,"uid":89402,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"888de12d4eb3faa39532b38d110ad0c82ece6851","tid":854543,"uid":9450,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T12:15:16.000Z","msg":"拎電話 <br />\n完"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T12:17:34.000Z","msg":"就係膽粗粗 唔夠膽開聲<br />\n又諗唔到個好啲既籍口<br />\n<br />\n如果佢問起 乜你成日周街問啲女仔拎電話架？<br />\n到時又唔知點答好"},{"pid":"54ff2e372e560bed4b2977959fee97c0a71ac3b0","tid":854543,"uid":89402,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"50183b484224f2c9f9976e783cef6e3c64fe630a","tid":854543,"uid":29070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"